Home to famous writers, thinkers, musicians and artists, Maryland’s largest city is a destination in its own right, with easy access to our nation’s capital. Your CSI DMC team looks forward to showcasing the fine dining, craft breweries and distilling, and the love of Old Bay that dominate this bustling port and lively downtown. A city with distinct flavor, Baltimore has been shaped by its vibrant neighborhoods, rich international immigrant culture, and industry. The CSI DMC Baltimore team puts you and your guests on the inside track to the best of what Baltimore can offer!
